                <h1>Efficient Background Jobs in Next.js: Boost Performance</h1>
                <p>Next.js background jobs allow developers to handle asynchronous tasks efficiently. By integrating task queues like Bull or Agenda, you can manage email sending, data processing, or scheduled tasks without blocking the main server thread. This enhances performance and ensures a smoother user experience in your Next.js applications.</p>
